  • public class MG4JClassParser
extends com.martiansoftware.jsap.stringparsers.ClassStringParser
    A small wrapper around JSAP's standard ClassStringParser. It tries to prefix it.unimi.di.big.mg4j.package. to the provided class name, making the specification of graph classes on the command line much easier.
